  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à FLTK</title>

    <para>
      FLTK (pronounced "fulltick") is a cross-platform C++ GUI toolkit.
      FLTK provides modern GUI functionality et supports 3D graphics via 
      OpenGL et its built-in GLUT emulation libraries used for creating 
      graphical user interfaces for applications.
    </para>

    &lfs75_checked;

